OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry through the evening and overnight.
OL,7,FSome prolonged spells of evening
OL,8,Fsunshine leading to some clear spells
OL,9,Fovernight meaning it might feel chilly
OL,10,Fin places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FDry with some lengthy sunshine
OL,13,Fto start but soon clouding over for
OL,14,Fthe Western Isles and west coast.
OL,15,FCloud spreading southeast to all
OL,16,Fthrough the afternoon with patchy
OL,17,Flight rain.
